description: Our smoky BBQ spice rub pairs unexpectedly well with sweet hoisin sauce for a sweet-and-spicy pork chop glaze. Tangy, juicy plum and jalapeño mirror that same flavor combo in a vibrant, sweet relish on top. Tender Swiss chard is folded into hearty forbidden rice for a colorful and tasty side.
